	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That animation would take up almost half the DMA, and half the VRAM with double buffering.<br /><br />@Sik, I agree.  Compression is not a good enough reason to use VRAM over CHR-ROM, because you're only going to be able to compress some of the data, some of the time.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
